text: Eunidia quadricincta is a species of beetle in the family Cerambycidae. It was described by Per Olof Christopher Aurivillius in 1911. It is known from Tanzania, Ethiopia, Somalia, and Kenya.BioLib.cz - Eunidia quadricincta. Retrieved on 8 September 2014. ==References== Category:Eunidiini Category:Beetles described in 1911
